Package: imputeTestbench
Type: Package
Title: Test Bench for the Comparison of Imputation Methods
Date: 2024-08-19
Maintainer: Marcus W. Beck <mbafs2012@gmail.com>
Contributor: Pranay Agrawal <agrawalpranay070@gmail.com>
Version: 4.0.0
Description: Provides a test bench for the comparison of missing data imputation 
    methods in uni-variate and multi-variate time series. The package now supports 
    high-performance computing using parallel processing and data.table, with options 
    for integrating Apache Spark. Imputation methods are compared using various 
    error metrics, with support for user-defined methods and metrics. A Shiny 
    dashboard is also available for visualization and management.
Imports:
